  "description": "Optimized for perfect fifth intervals. At Drama=0.85, the 3:2 frequency ratio between partials locks with zero beating. The formant is bright E-vowel, emphasizing the clarity of the interval. Play stacked fifths and hear the Pythagorean spiral \u2014 the oldest harmony in human music, rendered with digital precision.",
